OL,7,FEight months later, she returned,
OL,8,Fwhere the cancer was eventually
OL,9,Fdiagnosed and it was found to have
OL,10,Fgrown.
OL,12,FWithin a month, she was having surgery
OL,13,Fto have a mastectomy to remove both
OL,14,Fbreasts.
OL,16,FHospital chiefs admitted the surgery
OL,17,Fcould have been avoided if the cancer
OL,18,Fhad been caught sooner.
