OL,5,Cmissed
OL,7,FFollowing legal action led by medical
OL,8,Fnegligence specialists Hudgell
OL,9,FSolicitors, the Trust has agreed a six-
OL,10,Ffigure out-of-court damages settlement
OL,11,Ffor its failings.
OL,13,FSerena Russo said: "It was a tornado
OL,14,Fin my life. I've never had anything
OL,15,Fthing like it. It was hard, because at
OL,16,Fthe time I had young children at home.
OL,17,FSasha was two years old. It was
OL,18,Fdifficult.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
