OL,7,F"I want to say to the doctor, thank
OL,8,Fyou. I understand you are a human
OL,9,Fbeing and imperfect. You maybe have
OL,10,Fhad a bad day, but when you are with
OL,11,Fthe patient, you need to focus,
OL,12,Fbecause you either save a life, or you
OL,13,Fdon't.
OL,15,F"But I feel confident, I feel
OL,16,Ffeminine. I feel happy to live."
