OL,7,FMark Russo added: "I love the people
OL,8,Fthat work there because they've helped
OL,9,Fmy family. Our four children were born
OL,10,Fin Worthing Hospital and they've been
OL,11,Fevery single one of them.
OL,13,F"This one particular person, didn't
OL,14,Fserve the NHS well, and he didn't
OL,15,Fserve us well. But fundamentally, the
OL,16,FNHS is an absolute institution."
