OL,7,FProfessor Katie Urch, Chief Medical
OL,8,FOfficer at University Hospitals Sussex
OL,9,Fsaid: "We extend our sincere apologies
OL,10,Fto Mrs Russo and her family and wish
OL,11,Fher the very best for the future.
OL,13,F"We remain committed to improving
OL,14,Fservices for our patients. We are
OL,15,Fdoing this through increased
OL,16,Finvestment in staff and testing new
OL,17,Ftechnologies, to enable faster
OL,18,Fdiagnoses and the highest standards of
OL,19,Fsafety and quality."
